<br>
thanks, <br>
    Wuss <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=FAEBD7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub73.ezboard.com/utulaksz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TulakSZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>poon</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/13/01 6:09:36 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: very general eq question about AC</span><hr size=1> Agi does not effect the points of ac you get with a defense increase to the best of my knowledge.<br>
